These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, r&b
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, ivory
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | r&b |
| Color     | ivory | orange  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, electronic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Music-Genre    | rock      | electronic         |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly
City: marseilles, hamburg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Game   | monopoly | mah-jongg   |
| City       | hamburg  | marseilles |

 #################################

 
