.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, alhambra
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Flower      | dahlia | balloon-flower |
| Cigar   | alhambra        | havana  |

