.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-9::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, september
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, scooter
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Birthday   | september | october |
| Transport           | boat    | scooter     |

